1
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,720
Yaoyao, today you have to come with me here,

2
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:52,200
here, and here to check in.

3
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:53,240
OK, no problem.

4
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,720
What about you?

5
00:02:54,720 --> 00:02:56,000
Do you have any problems?

6
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:58,680
I'm following you guys, so it's definitely fine.

7
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,000
Smart choice.

8
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:01,960
We'll broaden your horizons today.

9
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,320
Is that OK?

10
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:05,800
Today,

11
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,730
Director Zhang is leading the way.

12
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:10,120
We are going for a city walk today.

13
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,880
City walk?

14
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,320
Exactly. The translation is

15
00:03:17,320 --> 00:03:18,440
to just

16
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,170
stroll around, wander, and do whatever you want.

17
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:27,760
Hurry.

18
00:03:27,760 --> 00:03:29,400
The good spots will be taken soon.

19
00:03:29,400 --> 00:03:30,460
Come here quickly.

20
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,520
It'll be here in a minute.

21
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,360
Get ready.

22
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,360
You take the picture.

23
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,090
I'll take it.

24
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:35,840
It's coming.

25
00:03:35,840 --> 00:03:37,160
Hurry, it's here.

26
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,040
It's so big.

27
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:41,800
Wow.

28
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,440
Did you get it?

29
00:03:51,000 --> 00:03:52,520
What did you shoot?

30
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:54,650
Where's the plane? Where's the focus?

31
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:56,360
I've only used it for a few days.

32
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:58,020
I'm not very familiar with it.

33
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,040
It's fine, Yiyi.

34
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,770
At least he learned a piece of modern technology.

35
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:03,400
Let's go.

36
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:05,000
Let's check in at the next place.

37
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,840
Let's go.

38
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,680
Let's go.

39
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,600
It's so cool today.

40
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,480
Hey, someone is doing a dragon dance.

41
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,600
Really.

42
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:21,399
Wow, cool.

43
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:33,520
Yaoyao, how did you find this kind of place?

44
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,200
You're the only one who knows how to plan.

45
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,480
No one else does.

46
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,760
Actually,

47
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:43,280
there is indeed one person among us three who doesn't know how.

48
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:45,010
I get mad just talking about it.

49
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:50,540
This bridge is much bigger than our Huitong Bridge back in the day.

50
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,440
We built this bridge ourselves.

51
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,640
The outside world wasn't optimistic at the time.

52
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:59,300
They said we didn't have the ability to build it.

53
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:03,200
You could say we built this bridge from scratch.

54
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,000
Look over there.

55
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,400
An old man is swimming.

56
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:13,640
He's in incredible shape.

57
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,400
It's about time.

58
00:05:25,400 --> 00:05:27,080
We still need to rush to the next spot.

59
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,480
Let's go. Hurry.

60
00:05:29,040 --> 00:05:30,000
Let's go.

61
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,680
What's wrong with the weather?

62
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:34,010
It's sunny one minute and cloudy the next.

63
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:38,140
Isn't the Burma Road known for having different weather every few miles?

64
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:50,240
This building is over 80 years old.

65
00:05:51,159 --> 00:05:52,620
You're even older than it.

66
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:28,080
This building looks a lot like Nanyang.

67
00:06:29,520 --> 00:06:30,960
Does it feel like home?

68
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,480
It really does.

69
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:38,640
Since it's so similar,

70
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,840
let's take a picture to commemorate it.

71
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,000
Let's take a photo.

72
00:06:44,159 --> 00:06:45,200
Look here.

73
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:49,280
One more.

74
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:54,240
Have a look.

75
00:06:58,880 --> 00:07:00,080
Why isn't he smiling?

76
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,200
Is he homesick?

77
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,480
Grandpa.

78
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:46,200
What's wrong?

79
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:51,080
Let's hide and see what this old fossil does.

80
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,280
Yiyi.

81
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,880
Yiyi!

82
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:04,800
Song Yao!

83
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:15,840
Yiyi!

84
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,120
Song Yao!

85
00:09:19,280 --> 00:09:20,080
Yiyi!

86
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:26,560
Hello.

87
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:27,970
Have you seen two girls?

88
00:09:28,680 --> 00:09:29,400
About this tall.

89
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:31,680
One wearing a red hat, the other a white hat.

90
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,400
No.

91
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:34,800
Why don't you just call them?

92
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,480
I don't have a phone.

93
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,000
Then find the police.

94
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,930
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

95
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:46,080
Sorry.

96
00:09:46,080 --> 00:09:47,320
Watch where you're going!

97
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,680
Hello, could you tell me how to get to the police station?

98
00:09:48,680 --> 00:09:50,410
I don't know, ask someone else.

99
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,960
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

100
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,680
Young man, where are you going?

101
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,840
Young man, where are you going?

102
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,480
The police station.

103
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,720
Go straight down this road for the police station.

104
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,480
Turn right at the first intersection and you'll be there.

105
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,480
[Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

106
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,640
Straight down this road.

107
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,400
Okay, thank you.

108
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:05,120
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

109
00:10:05,880 --> 00:10:06,120
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

110
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:06,680
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

111
00:10:06,680 --> 00:10:09,920
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

112
00:10:09,920 --> 00:10:11,650
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

113
00:10:11,920 --> 00:10:12,760
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

114
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,490
[Shacha Noodles 15 yuan/bowl]

115
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:34,880
Release him immediately.

116
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,760
Release him.

117
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:37,480
What are you yelling for?

118
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,200
I'll beat you up.

119
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:38,760
What are you yelling for?
